   </description>
   <indicator ascending="1" measure="1">
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN"># groups with improved internal management</narrative>
    </title>
    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Criteria used to say that these groups have improved their organizational developement include:
- the groups hold periodic meetings in well organised manner
- almost all the members participate in meetings and reports are written
- the groups have a bank book and submit report in the format required by HIC
- the groups diversify income generating activities
- their group improved their management skills and there are now less conflicts and more savings</narrative>
    </description>
